{"tid":2377854,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"救左隻重病貓仔 - Sumsum救助之路","createTime":"2021-01-24T03:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T17:45:16.000Z","uid":128849,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e48bf5e0ed1e3e0dadba59d97e4116f1f2ad35ff","tid":2377854,"uid":128849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"元朗親人流浪貓仔病得好嚴重<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2369729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2369729</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我係呢個post既樓主<br />\n係五日前我救左呢隻浪貓後<br />\n帶左佢去睇醫生<br />\n驗血結果顯示佢有貧血、脫水、器官發炎、貓愛滋<br />\n要馬上住院輸血吊鹽水<br />\n我地兩個人都冇遇過咁既情況<br />\n身上亦冇曬錢所以無法立刻入院<br />\n個晚，我地周圍出post求助<br />\n連登、天下貓貓、關於貓既group<br />\n總算籌到幾千蚊俾佢緊急入院<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqxovLz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoqxovLz.png&h=8a033f78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XsAxo5E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXsAxo5E.png&h=f15f27e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19/1 呢隻污糟貓一開頭個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCMXAsP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCMXAsP.jpg&h=ea9fe70c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n20/1 入院嗰日朝早，情況突然轉差，唔肯食野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYxWQ1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYxWQ1p.jpg&h=a84baa5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n20/1 入院第二次檢查後發現紅血球再跌3%，緊急輸血<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRr1hGO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRr1hGO.jpg&h=e19c83c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n21/1 輸血後第二日探佢，精神左少少但係對住我地都係嬲爆爆，唔知係咪嬲緊姐姐們帶佢黎呢度搞鳩佢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc7e9b845d8b4e669ed4c9d3367160c7a3c07c2","tid":2377854,"uid":128849,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmiZOQp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmiZOQp.jpg&h=a89b9763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22/1 雖然個腎係超聲波度檢查到異常，但因為精神太萎靡所以醫生恩準佢食兩啖肉泥，食得好激動好開心嗰時我話佢「你個嘴仔好污糟呀」，竟然發脾氣擰轉面唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要呵返話唔污糟呀靚仔貓呀先慢慢轉個頭過黎繼續食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/handup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mt1D4p0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMt1D4p0.jpg&h=24db878c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23/1 打針前夕，精神左好多，肯俾人摸下巴，嗲到兩個姐姐過左探病時間都唔願走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MgqtHcs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgqtHcs.jpg&h=eb356fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G9nWQ5R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG9nWQ5R.png&h=392eedd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一張係影到佢身上個心型<br />\n第二張係琴晚打完針之後發現佢身上有另一隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢好乖好叻完全冇掙扎冇慘叫，呢隻針好痛好痛，辛苦你啦Sumsum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1a3d5c4ffaed4e75f34b0491a459b8cbdaadcc","tid":2377854,"uid":128849,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:00:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/helpsumsumcat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhelpsumsumcat%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TakngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=c61d434f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/helpsumsumcat/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係Sumsum個fb page<br />\n詳細病情都係呢度每日update<br />\n簡單黎講，雖然因為Sumsum無腹水可抽，我地又冇錢做抽組織化驗，但驗血報告都顯示佢好高概率係Dry FIP，引起腎臟胰臟發炎，貧血脫水同黃疸情況都係因為病毒導致<br />\n<br />\n未來即將會係一場長期抗戰<br />\n我地唔係貓義工，只係兩個普通人<br />\n呢三個月時間內我地都會keep住update佢情況<br />\n希望大家可以幫Sumsum集氣加油<br />\n我相信佢對食物（esp吞拿魚）既熱愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢強韌既生命力<br />\n會話俾所有睇死佢會死既人知<br />\n唔好咁輕易放棄任何一條生命"},{"pid":"60a4f621e119b208810fe6fd449950252f7933e8","tid":2377854,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c412f49614a0eb5f4dac1a524c30b8d2cb377a4a","tid":2377854,"uid":128849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13929cb46b550fd1bdc36fb54aefc6233d8a5240","tid":2377854,"uid":293864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac07e09df530cc4b6496c414cd5cdd292987cfa","tid":2377854,"uid":293864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806f81e2250cc8ab9938d01ae78db9b423c2efa6","tid":2377854,"uid":293864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8327b256a02c7ae7fb1d372315ca320c02ead652","tid":2377854,"uid":293864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac